<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Staying home when sick isn&#8217;t possible for workers employed in a tough-it-out workplace culture without paid sick leave.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/karen-scott/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Karen Scott</a></span>, </dd>
