<article class="row hentry post-268475 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-health-care tag-paid-sick-leave tag-pandemic tag-public-health tag-trump-administration section-environment-and-health primary_topic-health" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/a-public-option-sustains-health-care-inequities-medicare-for-all-tackles-them/" title="A Public Option Sustains Health Care Inequities. Medicare for All Tackles Them.">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2020_0130-medicare-for-all-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Supporters of Sen. Bernie Sanders hold signs during an event on health care September 13, 2017, on Capitol Hill in Washington, D.C." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2020_0130-medicare-for-all-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2020_0130-medicare-for-all-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2020_0130-medicare-for-all-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2020_0130-medicare-for-all-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/2020_0130-medicare-for-all-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/op-ed/' rel='category' class='op-ed'>Op-Ed</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/environment-and-health/' rel='section' class='environment-and-health' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/a-public-option-sustains-health-care-inequities-medicare-for-all-tackles-them/">A Public Option Sustains Health Care Inequities. Medicare for All Tackles Them.</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Under the public option model, health services would still be rationed based on the ability to pay.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
